  <brief_title>The Effects of General Anesthesia on Microcirculation of Central and Peripheral Soft Tissue: a Comparison of Inhalational and Intravenous Anesthetics</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effects of General Anesthesia on Microcirculation of Central and Peripheral Soft Tissue: a Comparison of Inhalational and Intravenous Anesthetics</official_title>
